    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[Sweet or savoury? Chocolate or jam? Doughnuts provoke plenty of questions that divide millions of us every day. However, they may also be the key to answering one of the defining dilemmas of the 21st century – how do we tackle our appetite for endless economic growth? ]]></Value>
